Title: Zskera Vault: Ix
Description:
Wulferd spotted some pirates making their way into the vaults this morning. If we don't act fast, they'll strip the vault clean!

We're going into the vault immediately. There's no time to lose. Will you be joining us?
ObjectivesText: Enter and explore Zskera Vault: Ix

Objectives.Text: Speak with Pathfinder Jeb to enter the vault
